---
// Training journey section
---

<section id="training" class="s-training" data-intersect>
  <div class="s__inner">
    <h2 class="s__title">Training Journey</h2>
    <p class="s__subtitle">Strengthening problem-solving skills through intensive specialized training.</p>

    <div class="s-training__grid">
      <div class="s-training__card js-card">
        <div class="s-training__content">
          <div class="s-training__header">
            <div class="s-training__icon">
              <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M22 10v6M2 10l10-5 10 5-10 5z"></path>
                <path d="M6 12v5c3 3 9 3 12 0v-5"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="s-training__info">
              <h3>DSA & Concepts Training</h3>
              <div class="s-training__meta">
                <span class="s-training__org">CIPHERSCHOOL</span>
                <span class="s-training__date">Jan 2026 – Feb 2026</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="s-training__body">
            <p>
              Completed an intensive <strong>Data Structures & Algorithms</strong> training program focused on mastering fundamental and advanced coding concepts.
            </p>
            
            <div class="s-training__highlights">
              <h4><span class="icon">🏆</span> Key Highlights</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Guided by <strong>Mr. Adhiraj Chauhan</strong>.</li>
                <li>Mastered <strong>Arrays, Linked Lists, Trees, and Graphs</strong>.</li>
                <li>Solved complex algorithmic challenges with optimized time complexity.</li>
                <li>Focused on software engineering fundamentals and problem-solving.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="s-training__media">
          <div class="media-container media-container--slider">
            <img src="/images/winter.jpg" alt="Training with Class" class="img-1" />
            <img src="/images/sirji.jpeg" alt="Me with Mr. Adhiraj Chauhan" class="img-2" />
            <span class="media-label">Instructor & Class</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div><!-- .s-training__card -->

      <!-- AlgoTutor Card -->
      <div class="s-training__card js-card">
        <div class="s-training__content">
          <div class="s-training__header">
            <div class="s-training__icon" style="background: #ef4444;">
              <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="s-training__info">
              <h3>Competitive Programming Batch</h3>
              <div class="s-training__meta">
                <span class="s-training__org">AlgoTutor</span>
                <span class="s-training__date">June 2025 – July 2025</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="s-training__body">
            <p>
              Advanced training in <strong>Competitive Programming</strong> geared towards solving complex algorithmic puzzles, mastering advanced data structures, and optimizing code for time-critical contests.
            </p>
            
            <div class="s-training__highlights">
              <h4><span class="icon">🚀</span> Key Highlights</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Intensive problem-solving on platforms like <strong>Codeforces</strong>, <strong>CodeChef</strong>, and <strong>LeetCode</strong>.</li>
                <li>Mastered advanced optimization techniques and complex algorithmic paradigms.</li>
                <li>Participated in time-constrained coding contests to build algorithmic speed and efficiency.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="s-training__media">
          <div class="media-container">
            <img src="/images/summerpep.jpeg" alt="Competitive Programming Training" />
            <span class="media-label">Training Photo</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div><!-- .s-training__card -->
    </div><!-- .s-training__grid -->
  </div>
</section>

<style lang="scss">
  .s-training {
    padding: 10rem 0;
    background: color(primary);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;

    @include mq(phone) {
      padding: 5rem 1rem;
    }

    .s__inner {
      max-width: 1400px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 4rem;

      @include mq(phone) {
        padding: 0 1.5rem;
      }
    }

    .s__title {
      font: 700 6.5rem / 0.8 font-family(bigger);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: color(secondary);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      text-align: left;

      @include mq(tablet) {
        font-size: 5rem;
      }
      @include mq(phone) {
        font-size: 3rem;
      }
    }

    .s__subtitle {
      font: 400 1.5rem / 1.4 font-family(fraktion);
      color: color(secondary);
      text-align: left;
      margin-bottom: 5rem;
      opacity: 0.7;
      max-width: 800px;

      @include mq(phone) {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
      }
    }

    .s-training__grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 3rem;

      @include mq(tablet) {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 4rem;
      }
    }

    .s-training__card {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      background: rgba(color(secondary), 0.02);
      border: 1px solid color(secondary);
      transition: all 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
      
      &:hover {
        background: color(primary);
        transform: translateY(-10px);
        box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        
        .s-training__media img {
          transform: scale(1.05) rotate(1deg);
        }
      }
    }

    .s-training__content {
      flex: 1;
      padding: 3rem;
      
      @include mq(phone) {
        padding: 1.5rem;
      }
    }

    .s-training__header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;

      .s-training__icon {
        background: color(secondary);
        color: color(primary);
        padding: 1rem;
        border-radius: 12px;
        flex-shrink: 0;
      }

      .s-training__info {
        flex: 1;
      }

      h3 {
        font: 700 2.22rem / 1 font-family(fraktion);
        color: color(secondary);
        margin: 0 0 1rem;
        
        @include mq(phone) {
          font-size: 1.6rem;
        }
      }

      .s-training__meta {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        
        .s-training__org {
          font: 600 1rem font-family(fraktion);
          text-transform: uppercase;
          letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        }
        
        .s-training__date {
          font: 400 0.9rem font-family(fraktion);
          opacity: 0.6;
        }
      }
    }

    .s-training__body {
      color: color(secondary);
      line-height: 1.6;

      p { 
        font: 400 1.25rem font-family(fraktion);
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem; 
        opacity: 0.9;
        
        @include mq(phone) {
          font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
      }

      .s-training__highlights {
        h4 {
          font: 600 0.9rem font-family(fraktion);
          text-transform: uppercase;
          letter-spacing: 0.1em;
          margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
          display: flex;
          align-items: center;
          gap: 0.75rem;
          opacity: 0.6;
        }

        ul {
          list-style: none;
          padding: 0;
          
          li {
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font: 400 1.1rem font-family(fraktion);

            @include mq(phone) {
              font-size: 1rem;
            }

            &:before {
              content: '→';
              position: absolute;
              left: 0;
              color: color(secondary);
              opacity: 0.5;
            }

            strong {
              color: color(secondary);
              font-weight: 600;
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }

    .s-training__media {
      background: rgba(color(secondary), 0.05);
      border-top: 1px solid color(secondary);
      padding: 3rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      overflow: hidden;
      
      @include mq(phone) {
        padding: 1.5rem;
      }

      .media-container {
        position: relative;
        width: 100%;
        aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
        
        img {
          width: 100%;
          height: 100%;
          object-fit: cover;
          border: 1px solid color(secondary);
          transition: transform 0.8s ease;
        }

        .media-label {
          position: absolute;
          top: 1.5rem;
          right: 1.5rem;
          background: color(secondary);
          color: color(primary);
          padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
          font: 600 0.75rem font-family(fraktion);
          text-transform: uppercase;
          letter-spacing: 0.1em;
          z-index: 10;
        }
      }

      .media-container--slider {
        img {
          position: absolute;
          top: 0;
          left: 0;
          width: 100%;
          height: 100%;
          opacity: 0;
          transition: opacity 1.5s ease;
          
          &.img-1 {
            animation: slideFade 10s infinite;
          }
          
          &.img-2 {
            animation: slideFade 10s infinite 5s;
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }

  @keyframes slideFade {
    0%, 45% { opacity: 1; pointer-events: auto; }
    55%, 100% { opacity: 0; pointer-events: none; }
  }
</style>
